https://miro.com/careers/vacancy/5293876002/

As a Growth Product Design Director, you will be accelerating the experimentation culture and driving excellence in the Growth organization at Miro. It would combine building the world-class design team, strategizing the future of the domain with your cross-functional partners, constantly testing product hypotheses, and applying those learning to support sustainable business growth.

We treat "Growth" as the "distribution of value" across our existing and potential users. For success in this role, it's crucial to combine the love of the design craft with solid business acumen and empathy for millions of people who use our products daily.

As a Growth Product Design Director, you would strive for elegant and simple product solutions, while balancing ambitious business requirements and specific users needs.

If you are a seasoned design leader with a strong work ethic who would love to challenge yourself, we can make it work.
